{"tid":1550583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登班冷氣軍師完全垃撚圾","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T23:54:23.000Z","uid":56157,"like":70,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e23e67c04342415dec3b76b557a984da561a73","tid":1550583,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:41:43.000Z","msg":"今日各港鐵站都有人被人拉<br />\n但好多冷氣軍師根本完全唔知乜撚野事。<br />\n就第一時間衝出黎屌人做乜唔救人，前線又被人拉乜乜柒柒，勇武得啖笑，做咩唔快閃<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好明顯班冷氣軍師根本完全唔知發生乜撚野事</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n以今日沙田嗰班為例，其實係街坊<br />\n係人有打爆完地鐵啲機-&gt;警察黎-&gt;被街坊屌住走-&gt;走到一半突然失控衝前拉人-&gt;跟住先開拖，拉左幾個，拖左個入控制室-&gt;即刻有防暴到場<br />\n無人有Gear係情況下已經好盡力<br />\n唔好屌勇武，嗰班唔撚係勇武好無，要分既話佢地算係和理非比較多<br />\n<br />\n破壞地鐵設施嗰班一早已經撤左，係在場街坊憎黑警口頭屌，等於和理非集會咁樣<br />\n然後班狗失控攻擊街坊，班和理非街坊即時肯還拖已經好有進步，竟然被班冷氣軍師屌到一文不值<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">喂，你得把口都睇下直播啦，話比意見，發生乜事都唔知就先屌自己人，叫軍師？<br />\n分化撚就係。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"50c6d60d113e2713e8a41062245cc9a4ebdb2fef","tid":1550583,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:42:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"741c6bca7ac505d90bf6b0ee68e21797451accc0","tid":1550583,"uid":212622,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:43:30.000Z","msg":"樓主係冷氣軍師 垃圾"},{"pid":"bda9e3912bee7fc592f1117f124dae1f0586bd17","tid":1550583,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"741c6bca7ac505d90bf6b0ee68e21797451accc0","tid":1550583,"uid":212622,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:43:30.000Z","msg":"樓主係冷氣軍師 垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:44:18.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n即討post 最活躍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e634cac7f7e64265d383d4ccd0a9e7c875908aeb","tid":1550583,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"741c6bca7ac505d90bf6b0ee68e21797451accc0","tid":1550583,"uid":212622,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:43:30.000Z","msg":"樓主係冷氣軍師 垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"軍你老母，我未指點任何示威者點樣行動好唔好?<br />\n不過我係成日屌柒你班槍口對內既分化撚既"},{"pid":"083f383d7fdf8bb2414f3b044b3fc9e889161095","tid":1550583,"uid":228645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:47:16.000Z","msg":"其實無gear嘅情況下真係已經做得唔錯<br />\n有食個警棍嘅就會明無gear無盾係好難埋啲狗身<br />\n起碼今晚有救人嘅意識先"},{"pid":"d5d7b5b7a36a6c4f23c591a40877faec5f0afbcc","tid":1550583,"uid":66221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"741c6bca7ac505d90bf6b0ee68e21797451accc0","tid":1550583,"uid":212622,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:43:30.000Z","msg":"樓主係冷氣軍師 垃圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:49:04.000Z","msg":"一個信彈珠可以爆眼嘅人有資格出聲？"},{"pid":"53355fed5b535d9b9d428e14889316804b264042","tid":1550583,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"741c6bca7ac505d90bf6b0ee68e21797451accc0","tid":1550583,"uid":212622,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:43:30.000Z","msg":"樓主係冷氣軍師 垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:49:15.000Z","msg":"起碼唔係一邊自己享受冷氣， 一邊屌其他人唔夠勇武"},{"pid":"9e277c8352ca7ce175ce29291a77581343dcddd5","tid":1550583,"uid":53321,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:49:32.000Z","msg":"一到行動當日 連登上面大部分內容都廢"},{"pid":"927bc0f6efcb6cfa19b5308210dfc5817e4abf1c","tid":1550583,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5d7b5b7a36a6c4f23c591a40877faec5f0afbcc","tid":1550583,"uid":66221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"741c6bca7ac505d90bf6b0ee68e21797451accc0","tid":1550583,"uid":212622,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:43:30.000Z","msg":"樓主係冷氣軍師 垃圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:49:04.000Z","msg":"一個信彈珠可以爆眼嘅人有資格出聲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:49:46.000Z","msg":"擺明一毛黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8352602edb8073863752c1e05dd249e4c088f29a","tid":1550583,"uid":105067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e277c8352ca7ce175ce29291a77581343dcddd5","tid":1550583,"uid":53321,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:49:32.000Z","msg":"一到行動當日 連登上面大部分內容都廢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace65bc4e93afcf85795169a7cca96df8082024a","tid":1550583,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"樓主垃圾"},{"pid":"1f11dab06f9b2965305dbbfa5339db64447cf329","tid":1550583,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:50:54.000Z","msg":"唔係屌，但絕唔能夠話佢地係勇武，咁只會助長唔救人呢個風氣"},{"pid":"fb07a8962ac8e1383d8eef6c7106fad83aa777d8","tid":1550583,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:53:56.000Z","msg":"冷靜<br />\n唔好比對家搵到弱點<br />\n知道點樣分化我地<br />\n<br />\n和勇不分家<br />\n<br />\n每日檢討<br />\n負面標題易令運動陷入低潮<br />\n<br />\n此時此刻<br />\n一齊努力改善<br />\n<br />\n無人想手足犧牲<br />\n但槍口應對外 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果popo mon post<br />\n知道突衝、拉街坊、無gear 可以分化前線<br />\n又何必呢<br />\n唔好比佢地搵到新方法"},{"pid":"64c3bad247251733eee0eeb6b9bc71512a767413","tid":1550583,"uid":291946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:54:47.000Z","msg":"我頭先係NTP 同連城，的而且確大部份係街坊。<br />\n<br />\n得少部份勇少少嘅男仔拆閘同售票機，甚至好多人都冇口罩。班狗突然間失控擰轉頭噴椒同沖去撳住啲人，啲街坊都反應唔切。<br />\n<br />\n主要係啲人一開始只係圍爐唱歌，突然間有廢老係火車站用刀傷人，情況突然間激烈左，啲人都唔知發生緊咩事。"},{"pid":"102352778316665726d9dedfaf10616c86199c06","tid":1550583,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795f3454632770f3acef35baf9e9835c87ba56a4","tid":1550583,"uid":224479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e277c8352ca7ce175ce29291a77581343dcddd5","tid":1550583,"uid":53321,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:49:32.000Z","msg":"一到行動當日 連登上面大部分內容都廢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46d6d3cf662de1aee704d14acd6155c13081a28","tid":1550583,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfd17b099fb7d7a5ac1312f046a2343a1cfe242","tid":1550583,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e277c8352ca7ce175ce29291a77581343dcddd5","tid":1550583,"uid":53321,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:49:32.000Z","msg":"一到行動當日 連登上面大部分內容都廢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:09:01.000Z","msg":"班分化撚總之有理無理屌左自己人先<br />\n根本同一毛做埋啲野一樣"},{"pid":"a0a59704d9c9a57e64281bc758120a754182072c","tid":1550583,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" cl